'''{{Conjecture|Aleksei Mikhailovish Sytsevich}}''' (Russian: Алексей Михайлович Сицевич) is a man named '''Rhino'''.

==Biography==
{{MD|Aleksei Sytsevich (Earth-TRN971)}}
During Aleksei Sytsevich's criminal activities, he often ran into [[Spider-Man/Avengers Campus Recruitment|Spider-Man]], causing him to get logged into the [[W.E.B./Avengers Campus Recruitment|W.E.B.]] servers as a villain.{{Ref|WoSM1}}

==Relationships==
===Enemies===
*[[Spider-Man/Avengers Campus Recruitment|Spider-Man]]

==Trivia==
*In the comics, Alexei Sytsevich, also known by the alias '''Alex O'Hirn''', is a man that used a near-indestructible horned suit surgically bonded to his skin. Using his immense strength and durability, Alexei charges at anything in his way under the alias of Rhino, managing to become one of the many enemies [[Spider-Man]] faced during his crime fighting career.

